<section id="besuch" class="visit">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head">
      <div>
        <span class="eyebrow dark">Komm vorbei</span>
        <h2 class="display italic">Wir freuen uns auf dich.</h2>
      </div>
      <p>Reservieren ist empfohlen — gerade Freitag und Samstag wird's voll. Walk-ins sind aber jederzeit willkommen.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="visit-grid">
      <div class="visit-card">
        <span class="eyebrow tomato" style="font-size:28px">Öffnungszeiten</span>
        <h3>Jeden Abend<br/>für dich da.</h3>
        <table class="hours-table">
          <tbody>
            <tr><td>Montag</td><td>17:00 – 23:00</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Dienstag</td><td>17:00 – 23:00</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Mittwoch</td><td>17:00 – 23:00</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Donnerstag</td><td>17:00 – 23:00</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Freitag</td><td>17:00 – 01:00</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Samstag</td><td>17:00 – 01:00</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Sonntag</td><td>17:00 – 23:00</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <div class="visit-card dark">
        <span class="eyebrow" style="font-size:28px">So findest du uns</span>
        <h3>Neustadtring 30A,<br/><span class="y">Braunschweig.</span></h3>
        <ul class="address-list">
          <li>
            <span class="ico">
              <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z"/><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/></svg>
            </span>
            <span><strong>Adresse</strong>Neustadtring 30A, 38114 Braunschweig</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ico">
              <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72c.13.96.37 1.9.72 2.81a2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45c.91.35 1.85.59 2.81.72A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"/></svg>
            </span>
            <span><strong>Telefon</strong><a href="tel:053125079944" style="color:var(--lime)">0531 / 250 799 44</a></span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ico">
              <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M6 2 3 6v14a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h14a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V6l-3-4z"/><path d="M3 6h18"/><path d="M16 10a4 4 0 0 1-8 0"/></svg>
            </span>
            <span><strong>Abholung</strong>Online-Bestellung via Lieferando · Mo–So 17–22 Uhr</span>
          </li>
          <li>
